--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.3.2 (2020-11-30)
E: Do not create home directory for service user

* Version 0.3.1 (2020-11-27)
E: Improve Monit configuration file

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-11-24)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (loki_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-11-11)
B: Mark Loki datasource as default

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-11-10)
F: Add 'grafana' Ansible role dependency
F: Add Loki datasource to Grafana

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-11-09)
F: Initial release
